      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2630958/" class="title-link">以一篇演讲代书评，中国哲学的精神</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2630958"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/spinx/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2102060-341.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/spinx/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">阳极-半导体</span>
